## Coding Effects (mandatory)

### 1. Cursor Blink — logo + loading states

```tsx
// Logo format — always this exact structure:
<div style={{ fontSize: '15px', fontWeight: 700, letterSpacing: '-0.04em', color: 'var(--hz-ink)' }}>
  horion.pro<span className="hz-cursor" />
</div>
<p style={{ fontSize: '10px', color: 'var(--hz-muted)' }}>Reliability Engineering Platform</p>

// CSS (in globals.css):
// .hz-cursor { display:inline-block; width:8px; height:14px; background:var(--hz-ink);
//   vertical-align:middle; animation:hz-blink 1.1s step-end infinite; }
```

### 2. Grid Background — hero, pricing, stat bars

```tsx
<div className="hz-grid-bg" style={{ /* other styles */ }}>
// Dark mode handled automatically in globals.css
```

### 3. Scanline — terminal cards, code blocks only

```tsx
<div className="hz-scanline hz-term">
  {/* content renders above ::after pseudo-element scanline */}
</div>
```

### 4. Inline Code Token — file paths + function names in body text

```tsx
<span className="hz-tok">payment.go:203</span>
```

