## Dark / Light Mode

```tsx
// Toggle: add/remove class 'dark' on document.documentElement
// Persist: localStorage.setItem('hz-theme', 'dark' | 'light')
// Read: localStorage.getItem('hz-theme')
// FOUC prevention: inline script in root layout.tsx already handles this

// Smooth transition on all elements (already in globals.css):
// *, *::before, *::after { transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease; }
```

