## File Structure

```
apps/web/src/
├── app/
│   ├── globals.css              ← ALL --hz-* tokens + effects + base classes
│   ├── layout.tsx               ← JetBrains Mono + FOUC script (hz-theme key)
│   └── (dashboard)/layout.tsx   ← Sidebar shell with horion.pro logo
└── components/
    ├── ThemeToggle.tsx           ← uses hz-theme key
    └── ...                       ← all use --hz-* vars, no Tailwind colors
```

